subject: Tennis
French Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams struggled to defeat the 100th-ranked Klara Zakopalova, and James Blake, the 15th seed, was upset in the first round by Leonardo Mayer, a qualifier ranked 93rd.
